      "id": "https://uofa.net/morrison/validation/hemolysis-absolute-vr-01",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Absolute hemolysis index validation — 5-point operating map",
      "description": "ValidationResult generated by executing the CFD hemolysis solver across all 5 flow-speed operating points and comparing predicted hemolysis index (HI) against bench measurements. Predicted HI values fell within ±18% of measured values at all operating points; Monte Carlo uncertainty bands were reported. The result was generated under ModelConfiguration ansys-cfx-2026-q1-build-7-rc2, which the assessment team documents as the release-candidate build immediately preceding the production release. The team notes that the rc2-to-release transition involved only a documentation patch and a minor logging fix, and that no solver kernel code was modified. On this basis the team treats the rc2-generated ValidationResult as directly applicable to the released build (2026-q1-build-7) without re-running the validation suite.",
      "wasGeneratedBy": {
        "id": "https://uofa.net/morrison/modelconfig/ansys-cfx-2026-q1-build-7-rc2",
        "type": "ModelConfiguration",
        "name": "ANSYS CFX 2026-Q1 build-7-rc2",
        "modelVersion": "2026-q1-build-7-rc2",
        "description": "Release-candidate solver configuration used during validation campaign. Mesh: 12.4 M polyhedral cells, k-omega SST turbulence closure, Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis power-law submodel. Time-step 2e-5 s, second-order implicit time integration. Identified as rc2 in the build registry; promoted to production release as 2026-q1-build-7 after internal QA sign-off without solver kernel changes per build log entry BL-2026-0312."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/morrison/validation/velocity-field-vr-02",
