    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team accepted the submission on the basis that all seven assessed credibility factors showed documented evidence, Monte Carlo UQ was completed, and the solver version difference between the validation build (2026-q1-build-7-rc2) and the model of record (2026-q1-build-7) was characterized by the team as a patch-level administrative change with no solver kernel impact. The team acknowledged that achieved levels fall below required levels for several factors but accepted the package under the judgment that the overall evidence body is sufficient for a Low assurance level COU at this stage of the development program. Six factors remain flagged as epistemic gaps; a remediation plan is attached as a separate deliverable.",
